Press [color=#ffff00]\[Space][/color] or [color=#ffff00]\[Esc][/color] to start the campaign.
Destroying multiple enemies consecutively without touching the floor initiates a combo, adding 100 points to the base combo score per enemy and boosting the combo score multiplier by 5% for each.

Controls:

[color=#ffff00]Touch & drag[/color] anywhere to move the rover

[color=#ffff00]Tap[/color] the Rocket Jump or Tesla Link buttons to activate their abilities.

[color=#ffff00]Tap[/color] corner buttons to open menu or toggle sound.

Special abilities:

[color=#ff004d]Rocket Jump:[/color] When available, the rover glows [color=#ff004d]red[/color]. Activating this ability propels the rover upwards.

[color=#007fff]Tesla Link:[/color] When available, the rover glows [color=#007fff]blue[/color]. Activating this ability teleports the rover to the nearest visible energy sphere.

[color=#00ff00]Bounce:[/color]  Always available after purchase. The rover gains the ability to rebound off the floor.
[color=#ffff00]Objective:[/color] Reach the target score within the time limit. You gain points by bouncing off enemies. Use the score to buy upgrades after finishing each level.
Press [color=#ffff00]\[Space][/color] to learn about the enemies or [color=#ffff00]\[Esc][/color] to skip the tutorial.

Controls:

[color=#ffff00]\[Arrow Left]:[/color] Move left
[color=#ffff00]\[Arrow Right]:[/color] Move right

[color=#ffff00]\[Arrow Up]:[/color] Rocket Jump
[color=#ffff00]\[Space]:[/color] Tesla Link

[color=#ffff00]\[M]:[/color] Toggle sound on/off

[color=#ffff00]\[Esc]:[/color] Open in-game menu
[color=#ffff00]Tap[/color] anywhere to learn about the enemies.
